items.title: Urban and Regional Planning Resources
items.content_text:
### Platforms and Software Resources / Urban Design Tools and Platforms

*   [CityEngine](https://www.esri.com/en-us/arcgis/products/arcgis-cityengine/overview) - CityEngine is advanced 3D modeling software for creating huge, interactive and immersive urban environments in less time than traditional modeling techniques. The cities you create using CityEngine can be based on real-world GIS data and the procedural rules that can help quickly create [streets (⭐205)](https://github.com/d-wasserman/Complete_Street_Rule) & [buildings](https://www.arcgis.com/home/group.html?id=01695af30a384c1e823fa4d72497309d#overview).
items.content_html:
